## LogLevel enum

### LogLevel enum

Mapping of log level abbreviation to canonical log level. Supported levels are reduce to limit color variation.

<b>Signature</b>

```typescript
export declare enum LogLevel 
```
<b>Import</b>

```typescript
import { LogLevel } from '@grafana/data';
```
